                <h3 class="region-card__title">Dampier Strait & Fam Islands</h3>
                <p class="region-card__desc">
                  The most accessible and dive-rich region. The Dampier Strait
                  between Waigeo and Batanta hosts the highest concentration of
                  world-class dive sites, including Cape Kri, Blue Magic, and
                  the famous manta cleaning stations.
                </p>
                <div class="region-card__highlights">
