                  Iconic mushroom-shaped karst islands rising from turquoise
                  lagoons. The Wayag viewpoint hike reveals one of the world's
                  most photographed seascapes. Waigeo's western coast offers
                  bird-of-paradise treks at dawn.
                </p>
                <div class="region-card__highlights">
