                Strait, clear water for photography, and comfortable crossings
                to Wayag and Misool.
              </p>

              <p>
                <strong>December–February</strong> represents peak season. Weather
                is most stable, visibility is exceptional, and manta activity reaches
                its height.
              </p>

              <p>
                <strong>October–November</strong> offers excellent conditions with
                fewer boats.
              </p>

              <p>
                <strong>March–April</strong> sees conditions gradually shifting but
                still very good diving.
              </p>

              <h3>Shoulder Season: May & September</h3>
